          "process_md": "Applicants can submit their applications online at [www.nlm.udyamimitra.in](https://nlm.udyamimitra.in/). The process involves the following steps:\n\n  - Screening of Applications by the State Implementing Agency.\n  - Loan Approval by the designated lender.\n  - Recommendation by the State Level Executive Committee (SLEC).\n  - Sanction of Subsidy by the Animal Husbandry and Dairying Department.\n  - For detailed guidelines on the release of subsidy, please visit the department’s website [www.dahd.nic.in](https://dahd.gov.in/) or contact the State Animal Husbandry Department.\n<br>\n\n"
